Great combat sim. Thank you for addressing the last glitch that came with the update (terrain rendering), but with that glitch addressed it now has a new one. This latest glitch occurs when approaching the field for landing. When airspeed is reduced enough to drop landing gear, and the gear is dropped, all forward momentum completely stops and the jet stalls and falls straight to the ground. There is no way to recover the aircraft before crashing unless you approach the field at a very high altitude and then slowly drop the nose and dive in order to get enough airspeed for viable lift and recovery.
